    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>As an action, the paladin channels the darkest emotions and focuses them into a burst of magical menace. Each creature of the paladin's choice within 30 feet of the paladin must make a Wisdom saving throw if it can see the paladin. On a failed save, the target is &amp;Reference[condition=frightened] of the paladin for 1 minute. If a creature &amp;Reference[condition=frightened] by this effect ends its turn more than 30 feet away from the paladin, it can attempt another Wisdom saving throw to end the effect on it.</p></div>",
